    "Thus, students were asked to write two summaries: one at the beginning and another at the end of the session.",
    "To evaluate the improvement in the summaries, the course instructor and a research assistant compared the original summary with the revised version.",
    "Table 3 presents a scoring rubric for assessing summary quality, which is based on two primary criteria: Content and Thinking.",
